title: Robert Dilts - Sleight of Mouth
description:
In this 4 divx set by Robert Dilts you will: 

Learn 16 Ways to reframe anything you want and do it right. 

Learn how to recognize beliefs and how to change beliefs covertly or overtly. 

Learn how to gently point people in your direction and get them to do what you want them to do.

Learn how to automatically use these patterns.

Learn about how to deal with rejections and get them to agree with you. 

What Beliefs are and how to work with beliefs 

How to speak the language of beliefs to get what you want 

And much much more...
